reviewText: Again, I'm not sure who is watching these movies, but this movie was bearable. I actually finished it. The production sucked a bit and it didn't flow well, but the acting was pretty good surprisingly. I've seen worst!! I see the potential here.
A really great movie. I enjoyed it and it's based on a true story.
This was an enjoyable movie. I really loved it!
Such a compelling story! I didn't want it to end.
I really liked this movie.  It had drama and suspense all of the good stuff that you are looking for in a good movie.  If you are looking for an up and coming new director check out this movie.
This movie was well made and told a good story too! I hope to hear more from the filmmakers and actors involved.
